<br>
-they never forget who attacked them, and their group members.<br>
-they never hesitate<br>
-they never get lost<br>
-they never fizzle a spell<br>
-they never get &quot;sit&quot; agro<br>
-they cast againt invis players<br>
-they never go LD<br>
-they don't have to mem spells<br>
-they never interupt themselves by moving<br>
-they are next to impossible to interrupt<br>
-they can cast through walls<br>
-they can wield melee weapons<br>
-they hit as often as monks<br>
-they have AC and HPs of tanks<br>
-they regen like crazy<br>
-they have seemingly endless mana<br>
-they always cast in range<br>
-they always attack you in range<br>
-they can SOW each other indoors<br>
-they have access to rare spells<br>
-they have no spell refresh restrictions<br>
-they don't have to meditate<br>
-they are immune to many spells<br>
-they can see invis many of them<br>
-they can summon players (funny spell that summon?)<br>
-they can warp to you from hundreds of feet away<br>
-they cast spells that are outside their &quot;class&quot;<br>
-their gate spells never seem to collapse<br>
-they cast spells beyond their level<br>
-they melee better than any PC<br>
-they don't have a level cap at which they can cast and land spells on PC's above their level.<br>
<br>
If only PC casters were so balanced after a single patch I don't think any caster would be complaining.  <br>
<br>
IMO they broke the game and have gone into the &quot;OOOPSS... oh wait, lets leave it in and just tune it back a bit.&quot;  Typical to unleash a demon on the players and then tell him to play nice instead of just removing it.<br>
<br>
I hope they not only make the casters cast within their levels but also have them adjusted in their hps and Ac and their melee should be much less than it currently is.  It doesn't have to be as &quot;pitifull&quot; as PC caster melee, hps, ac etc but it should not be equal to their  melee brethern.<br>
<br>
You just don't cram a change like that into the game this far into it and then tell all your players, well we will tone it down and fix any wild inconsitencies these &quot;nifty&quot; new mobs have.  Isn't this fun?!!?  Oh and by the way, we hope to be getting back to you PC caster balancing when we are done tuninng all these fun NPC casters and rebalancing all NPC caster encounters in the game.  Now your NPC counterparts got their uberfication overnight but we have taken 6 months to come around to healing and I wouldn't expect too much there, don't want to upset the delicate balance between classes.  Not to mention that because of the new nukes and abilities of your NPC mobs CLERICS and CHANTERS just became EVEN MORE ESSENTIAL.. hell even Paladins are better because of stun and so forth.. <br>
<br>
thank you..<br>
<br>
Europa<br>
